Jon Feltheimer Net Worth | Celebrity Net Worth           Celebrity Net Worth  Search Random  Jon Feltheimer Net WorthHow much is Jon Feltheimer Worth? in Richest Businessmen › CEOsShare on FacebookShare on TwitterRandom CelebrityJon Feltheimer net worth:$30 Million Jon Feltheimer is an American businessman who has a net worth of $30 million. Jon Feltheimer has earned his net worth as the Chief Executive Officer of Lions Gate Entertainment, since 2000, as well as the Co-Chairman of the Board since June 2005. This company is a North American entertainment company, which was formed in Vancouver, British Columbia in 1997, and is headquartered in Santa Monica, California. He was born on September 2, 1951 in Brooklyn, New York. Jon earned his a BA in economics that included honors from Washington University in St. Louis. He led Lions Gate Entertainment into one of the leading Canadian independent film entertainment studio. He also worked at Sony Pictures Entertainment from 1991 to 1999. At Sony he also served as the Founder and President of TriStar Television from 1991 to 1993, and as President of Columbia TriStar Television from 1993 to 1995, as well as the President of Columbia TriStar Television Group and Executive Vice President of Sony Pictures Entertainment from 1995 to 1999. His 25 years plus of experience in the entertainment industry, brings an unparalleled level of strategic and operational experience to the Board, and an in-depth understanding of the industry, as well as invaluable relationships in the business and entertainment community. Jon FeltheimerBusinesspersonDate of BirthSep 2, 1951 (65 years old)ProfessionBusinessperson, Film ProducerNationalityUnited States of AmericaMore CEOs Martin Shkreli Net Worth  Brian Sheth Net Worth  Don Blankenship Net Worth  Peter Szulczewski Net Worth  Apoorva Mehta Net Worth  Dana White Net Worth  Jimmy Iovine Net Worth  Steve Jobs Net Worth  Mark Hurd Net Worth  Mark Zuckerberg Net Worth  Share on FacebookAll net worths 